(1, 1, '2012-12-11 16:47:26', '2012-12-11 16:47:26', 'The Deconstruction is an experimental, decentralized event project that attempts to explore the core of creativity and problem-solving.  Our belief is that powerful new ideas are not manifested through unlimited means and resources...they are pieced together using found material, collaboration, and by rethinking what''s right in front of you.  The Deconstruction is a not for profit project that utilizes this same ideology.\r\n\r\nWe also think the process should be fun...\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'El Manifesto', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hello-world', '', '', '2013-02-08 08:57:09', '2013-02-08 08:57:09', '', 0, 'http://thedecon.wpengine.com/?p=1', 0, 'post', '', 1),
