(30, 3, '2012-12-20 08:01:16', '2012-12-20 08:01:16', '<div class="home_content">\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-315" style="text-align: center; margin-left: 40px;" alt="Home image" src="http://thedeconstruction.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/homecenterimage-1-e1359334417222.jpg" width="776" height="546" />\r\nThe Deconstruction is a 48-hour creative event for Makers, Artists, Students, Programmers, Problem-Solvers, Designers, Performers, Robots…basically anyone!  It challenges teams of participants to "deconstruct" the world around them by rethinking, remixing, and creating something new from existing objects and ideas.\r\n\r\nThe Deconstruction is an experimental decentralized event. People anywhere and everywhere can participate, physically and digitally, through live-streaming and social media.  The entire event will be broadcast continuously on-line from Feb 22nd-24th and feature participants (you?), special guests, and live conversations about the creative process, new ideas, and making new ideas real. Sound interesting? <strong><a title="How It Works" href="http://thedeconstruction.org/manifesto/">Learn</a><a title="How It Works" href="http://thedeconstruction.org/manifesto/"> more here</a>. </strong>Or better yet.....\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;"><a class=" button" title="Register" href="http://thedeconstruction.org/register/">Register Your Team</a></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;"></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;"></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;"></div>', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'home', '', '', '2013-02-14 17:12:16', '2013-02-14 17:12:16', '', 0, 'http://staging.thedeconstruction.org/?page_id=30', 0, 'page', '', 0),
